@host = http://localhost:5261

### Login — use data.user.id for profile URLs
POST {{host}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@demo.local",
  "password": "Admin@123!"
}

### Profile (userId = GUID from data.user.id)
@userId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
GET {{host}}/api/users/profile?userId={{userId}}

### Products — list
GET {{host}}/api/products?page=1&pageSize=10
